OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Flargely cloudy through this evening
OL,7,Fand overnight, as rain slowly dies out
OL,8,Fduring the evening. Perhaps some clear
OL,9,Fspells developing in northern parts,
OL,10,Fleading to a possible frost in prone
OL,11,Fspots. Light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FCloud thinning Saturday
OL,14,Fmorning, turning brighter before a
OL,15,Fband of showers progresses eastward in
OL,16,Fthe afternoon. Skies clearing later,
OL,17,Fwith a possible early frost, then
OL,18,Ffurther light rain overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
